Happy Birthday with Cupcakes and Wine Gift Set
List.Description:
Cupcakes and wine make an absolutely delicious birthday gift. This gift includes Stonewall Kitchen's wonderfully moist cupcake mix and deliciously creamy frosting. Coupled with a bottle of Cupcake Chardonnay and the birthday celebration is ready to begin!

Wine Gift Includes:

  • Cupcake Vineyards Chardonnay:
    This Chardonnay offers decadent levels of butter, cream, bright citrus and vanilla which melt into a balance of oak and subtle spice.

  • Stonewall Kitchen's Chocolate Coconut Cupcake and Frosting Mixes
  • Multi-Color Non-Pareils
  • 12 white candles
  • 12 paper liners
  • Festive Greet Sheet

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.

govino Go Anywhere Flute - Set of 4
List.Description:
The shatter-proof govino wine flute was designed both for ultimate convenience and an authentic wine tasting experience. Made from a food-safe, 100% BPA-free polymer that reflects color and projects aromatics like crystal, govino glasses are not your same old plastic patio wine glass. An ergonomic thumb hold makes sipping a breeze! The glass flexes a little in your hand, but will not break, even if it takes a tumble. Hand wash your govino flutes to re-use them, or simply recycle them when done. Comes as a set of four flutes. P> Hand-wash only. 8oz each. Made in the USA.
